OL,3,CSeaside big wheel under threat
OL,5,FTorquay's seafront big wheel, which
OL,6,Fhas been a feature of Devon's summer
OL,7,Flandscape for more than a decade,
OL,8,Fcould be missing in 2024.
OL,10,FOperators have submitted their annual
OL,11,Fapplication to have the big wheel in
OL,12,Fits usual place alongside the Princess
OL,13,FTheatre from now until October.
OL,15,FBut planning officers at Torbay
OL,16,FCouncil are advising members of the
OL,17,Fplanning committee to say no to the
OL,18,F'alien and incongruous' wheel.
