OL,3,CSeaside big wheel under threat
OL,5,FIt says vehicles park in the gardens,
OL,6,Ftrees have been taken down to allow
OL,7,Faccess and the heritage impacts of the
OL,8,Fwheel have been downplayed.
OL,10,FIt added: "There are no very special
OL,11,Fcircumstances to allow the wheel in
OL,12,Fthis local green space."
OL,14,FHistoric England has also said it is
OL,15,F'strongly concerned' about the harm
OL,16,Fthe wheel does to heritage assets.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
