OL,3,CSeaside big wheel under threat
OL,5,FThe council's own principal historic
OL,6,Fenvironment officer said: "It is clear
OL,7,Fthat the proposed development would
OL,8,Fcause clear harm to a number of
OL,9,Fidentified heritage assets and that
OL,10,Fthe proposals in their current form
OL,11,Fwould neither preserve nor enhance the
OL,12,Fcharacter or appearance of the
OL,13,Fidentified conservation area.
OL,15,F"The wheel and its associated
OL,16,Fstructures appear as alien and
OL,17,Fincongruous features.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
