OL,3,CSeaside big wheel under threat
OL,5,F"Notwithstanding this, the council
OL,6,Freceived objections to the application
OL,7,Ffrom Historic England, Torbay Heritage
OL,8,FTrust and the council's principal
OL,9,Fhistoric environment officer.
OL,11,F"In this case, officers have concluded
OL,12,Fthat the harm to local heritage
OL,13,Foutweighs the benefits presented.
OL,15,F"Officer recommendation to the
OL,16,Fplanning committee is to refuse
OL,17,Fplanning permission."
OL,19,FA decision is expected to be made on
OL,20,Fthe evening of Monday 29 April.
